lead_paragraph: Four clubs, including former South American champions Santos and Europa League holders Sevilla, have been fined for breaking FIFA's rules on third party influence, soccer's governing body said Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Four Clubs Fined for Breaking Third-Party Rules
